OL,3,CPrison deaths linked to powerful
OL,4,Copioid drug
OL,6,FThe presence of a strong opioid drug
OL,7,Flinks four out of the six sudden
OL,8,Fdeaths reported at Parc Prison in
OL,9,FBridgend, says South Wales Police.
OL,11,Fat the south Wales prison since the
OL,12,Fend of February.
OL,14,FFour of the deaths are being
OL,15,Finvestigated and believed to be drug
OL,16,Frelated, with the other two being
OL,17,Ftreated as non-suspicious.
OL,19,FThe substances in question are
OL,20,Fnitazenes.
