OL,3,CPrison deaths linked to powerful
OL,4,Copioid drug
OL,6,FA recent ITV Wales investigation
OL,7,Frevealed health officials are becoming
OL,8,F"severely concerned" about the
OL,9,Fincreasing emergence of nitazenes on
OL,10,Fthe illegal market.
OL,12,FNitazenes are synthetic opioids that
OL,13,Fcan be 500 times stronger than
OL,14,Fmorphine. They can be injected,
OL,15,Finhaled or swallowed, in tablet form.
OL,17,FTheir incredible strength makes them
OL,18,Fextremely dangerous - and health
OL,19,Fofficials are also seeing evidence of
OL,20,Fthem being mixed in with other drugs.
