OL,6,FThe drug 'spice' has also been
OL,7,Fidentified in two out of the four
OL,8,Fdeaths.
OL,10,FIn a statement, Detective Steve Jones
OL,11,Ffrom South Wales Police said: "At this
OL,12,Fstage we cannot confirm that the four
OL,13,Fdeaths are connected to any specific
OL,14,Fdrug however a fast-track process has
OL,15,Fbeen undertaken and identified the
OL,16,Fpresence of Nitazene based substances
OL,17,Fin connection with all four deaths.
OL,19,F"Spice has been identified in two of
OL,20,Fthe four deaths."
