OL,6,FHe added: "Postmortems have been
OL,7,Fcompleted on two of the four men and
OL,8,Fat this stage cause of death is
OL,9,Finconclusive and we are awaiting
OL,10,Ftoxicology. The other two men are
OL,11,Fawaiting a postmortem."
OL,13,FThe six deaths are among a total of 20
OL,14,Fdeaths at the prison the body has been
OL,15,Fnotified of, and begun investigating,
OL,16,Fsince January 2022.
OL,18,FIn an earlier statement, Ombudsman
OL,19,FAdrian Usher urged all prisoners in
OL,20,Fpossession of spice to dispose of it
OL,21,Fimmediately.
