OL,6,FThe prison is run by private security
OL,7,Ffirm G4S and is one of the largest
OL,8,Fprisons in the UK, housing more than
OL,9,F1,700 inmates.
OL,11,FThe Prisons and Probation Ombudsman
OL,12,Fconfirmed the names of the two Parc
OL,13,Fprisoners who died on February 27,
OL,14,FJason Hussey and John Rose, but has
OL,15,Fnot released the names of the four
OL,16,Finmates who have died since.
